Will be UPDATE

XileTrade is a free tool that provide help while playing on POE leagues.
USAGE: To configure or close the program, use right click on system tray icon.
BE AWARE: This program is free, closed-source for now and still in development.
IF YOU LIKE the program or/and want more features, you can help the project by donating.

Need .NETFramework at least Version v4.6 to work on your computer :
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=48136

This pricing-tool use official trade website of Path of exile ! It will be update later to support 
each language provided by the game.

